  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/localize\", \"name\": \"@angular/localize\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/localize/init\", \"name\": \"@angular/localize/init\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/localize\">@angular/localize</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/localize/init/PACKAGE.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/localize/init/PACKAGE.md\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n<header class=\"api-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"angularlocalizeinit\">@angular/localize/init<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#angularlocalizeinit\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n  <label class=\"api-type-label NaN\">entry-point</label>\n  \n  \n  \n</header>\n\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\"><p>The <code>@angular/localize</code> package exposes the <code><a href=\"api/localize/init/$localize\" class=\"code-anchor\">$localize</a></code> function in the global namespace, which can\nbe used to tag i18n messages in your code that needs to be translated.</p>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"入口点的导出\">入口点的导出<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#入口点的导出\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"entry-point-exports\">Entry point exports<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#entry-point-exports\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"类型\">类型<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#类型\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"types\">Types<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/localize/init#types\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/localize/init/$localize\">$localize</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p>Tag a template literal string for localization.</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/localize\n - api/localize/init/$localize\n - api/localize/init/LocalizeFn\n - api/localize/init/TranslateFn\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/localize\n - api/localize/init#angularlocalizeinit\n - api/localize/init#entry-point-exports\n - api/localize/init#types\n - api/localize/init#入口点的导出\n - api/localize/init#类型\n - api/localize/init/$localize\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/localize/init/PACKAGE.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n